isRegistrar(address).notice: Check if an account has registrar role.

isRenewer(address).notice: Check if an account has renewer role.

ownerOf(uint256).notice: Gets the owner of the specified domain.

reclaim(uint256,address).notice: Reclaim ownership of a domain in RNS.

register(bytes32,address,uint256).notice: Registers a domain in RNS for a given duration.

removeRegistrar(address).notice: Remove an account's access to registrar role.

removeRenewer(address).notice: Remove an account's access to renewer role.

renew(bytes32,uint256).notice: Renew a domain for a given duraiton.

setRootResolver(address).notice: set root node resolver in RNS.

setRootTTL(uint64).notice: set root node ttl in RNS.
